			"mode": 0,
			"properties": {"text": ""},
			"widgets_values": [
				"📹 ENHANCED VIDEO UPSCALE WORKFLOW (with RIFE Interpolation)\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n🎯 FEATURES:\n   ✅ 3 Upscale Options: None / 2x / 1080P\n   ✅ RIFE Frame Interpolation: 24fps → 48fps (smoother motion)\n   ✅ Manual FPS Control (no auto-calculation errors!)\n   ✅ Strategic VRAM Management\n\n📋 INSTRUCTIONS:\n\n1️⃣ UPLOAD VIDEO:\n   • Click 'Load Video' node → Choose video file\n   • Supports: MP4, MOV, AVI, WebM\n   • Max recommended: 30 seconds for 24GB VRAM\n\n2️⃣ SELECT UPSCALE OPTION (Node: Upscale Mode):\n   • 0: No upscale (original resolution) - Fastest\n   • 1: 2x upscale (480p→960p, 720p→1440p) - Best quality\n   • 2: Fixed 1080P output - For platform requirements\n\n3️⃣ RIFE INTERPOLATION:\n   • Enable RIFE: true/false (Node: Enable RIFE)\n   • RIFE Multiplier: 2 = double FPS (24→48, 30→60)\n   • Output FPS: Set manually (e.g., 48 if source=24 and multiplier=2)\n   ⚠️ IMPORTANT: If RIFE disabled, set Output FPS = source FPS!\n\n4️⃣ QUEUE PROMPT → Wait → Download result!\n\n💾 VRAM GUIDE (24GB):\n   • No upscale + No RIFE:  ~3-5GB   ⚡ Super fast\n   • 2x upscale + No RIFE:  ~8-10GB  ✅ Recommended\n   • 2x upscale + RIFE:     ~10-13GB ✅ Best quality\n   • 1080P + RIFE:          ~12-16GB ⚠️ Heavy\n\n⏱️ PROCESSING TIME (per 10s):\n   • No upscale: ~30 sec\n   • 2x upscale: ~2-3 min\n   • 2x + RIFE:  ~3-4 min\n   • 1080P + RIFE: ~4-5 min"
			],
			"color": "#233",
			"bgcolor": "#355"
		},
		{
			"id": 4,
