			"widgets_values": [
				"⚙️ UPSCALE OPTIONS EXPLAINED\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n🔹 Option 0 - NO UPSCALE:\n   Use when: Source video already good quality\n   Speed: ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ | VRAM: ~3-5GB\n\n🔹 Option 1 - 2X UPSCALE (FlashVSR):\n   Use when: Need highest quality, any resolution\n   Speed: ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | VRAM: ~8-13GB\n   Output: Width×2, Height×2\n\n🔹 Option 2 - FIXED 1080P (Auto-Adapt):\n   Use when: Platform requires ~1080P size (YouTube/TikTok)\n   Speed: ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | VRAM: ~10-16GB\n   Output: Auto-adapts to orientation!\n   • Portrait (480×832) → 1101×1920 (keeps ratio)\n   • Landscape (1920×1080) → 1920×1080\n   • Longest side always = 1920 pixels"
			],
