		{
			"id": 17,
			"type": "Note",
			"pos": [1950, 550],
			"size": [400, 240],
			"flags": {},
			"order": 15,
			"mode": 0,
			"properties": {"text": ""},
			"widgets_values": [
				"🎬 RIFE INTERPOLATION SETTINGS\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n✨ WHAT IS RIFE?\n   AI-powered frame interpolation that creates smooth\n   in-between frames for buttery-smooth motion\n\n⚙️ SETTINGS:\n   • Model: rife49.pth (latest, best quality)\n   • Multiplier: 2 (doubles FPS: 24→48, 30→60)\n   • Fast mode: false (quality over speed)\n   • Ensemble: true (smooth blending)\n\n📊 BENEFITS:\n   ✅ Smoother motion (no stuttering)\n   ✅ Better for slow-motion\n   ✅ More cinematic feel\n   ✅ Higher engagement on social media\n\n⚠️ COST:\n   • VRAM: +2-3GB\n   • Time: +30-40%\n   • File size: +40-50% (more frames)\n\n💡 RECOMMENDED FOR:\n   TikTok, Instagram Reels, YouTube Shorts"
			],
			"color": "#233",
			"bgcolor": "#355"
		},
		{
			"id": 18,
			"type": "Note",
			"pos": [2600, 1350],
			"size": [400, 260],
			"flags": {},
			"order": 16,
			"mode": 0,
			"properties": {"text": ""},
			"widgets_values": [
				"💾 OUTPUT SETTINGS\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n📊 QUALITY (CRF):\n   • 18: High quality, large file ✅ Recommended\n   • 21: Balanced\n   • 23: Good, smaller file\n   Lower = Better quality\n\n🎞️ FRAME RATE:\n   Manual control via 'Output FPS' node:\n   • No RIFE: Set to source FPS (24/30/60)\n   • With RIFE 2x: Set to source × 2 (48/60/120)\n   • With RIFE 3x: Set to source × 3 (72/90/180)\n   \n   Common combinations:\n   24 fps + RIFE 2x = 48 fps output ✅\n   30 fps + RIFE 2x = 60 fps output ✅\n   60 fps + RIFE 2x = 120 fps output\n\n📁 FORMAT:\n   • H.264 MP4 (best compatibility)\n   • YUV420P color space\n\n💾 OUTPUT LOCATION:\n   ComfyUI/output/ folder\n\n📝 FILENAME:\n   Default: upscaled_enhanced_XXXXX.mp4\n   Change prefix above if needed\n\n✅ ESTIMATED FILE SIZE (per minute):\n   • 480p: ~15-25 MB\n   • 720p: ~30-50 MB\n   • 1080p: ~60-100 MB\n   • 1080p + RIFE: ~90-150 MB"
			],
